      "content": "<p>There are many types of light (also known as <a href=\"http://rubineducation.org/glossary/electromagnetic-radiation\" target=\"_blank\">electromagnetic radiation</a>): radio waves, infrared, visible, ultraviolet (UV), X-rays, etc. The type of light we can see with our eyes is called “visible” light.</p>",
